prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor painting of a humorous birthday card front. The scene features illustrated cartoon versions of the couple from the reference photo against a clean white background with subtle paper texture and organic paint bleeds.

On the left, an illustrated cartoon character of Lao Lao, an East Asian woman with long, straight dark brown hair, a warm smile, and thin gold-rimmed glasses, is wearing a black long-sleeved shirt. She is holding a giant, comically oversized cup of boba tea, struggling to lift it with a funny, strained expression.

On the right, an illustrated cartoon character of Jordan, an East Asian man with spiky, textured dark hair, is wearing a maroon t-shirt. He has a wide, happy grin and is comically attempting to take a massive bite out of a gigantic bahn mi that's so large it's bending in the middle.

Between them, on a small table, sits a steaming bowl of Chinese porridge with a spoon sticking out. The overall composition is chaotic, fun, and food-focused, with soft, flowing watercolor colors and artistic brush strokes.

Centered on the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! May your day be as extra as our cravings."

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
